Product.MarketingTextHeader: The new Philips FC6092 (12V) for easy car cleaning gives you the optimal freedom of cordless cleaning and the special car-cleaning kit includes a car plug for unlimited runtime so you can clean you car thoroughly in one go!

Feature.FeatureGlossary: The Philips Mini Vac’s cyclonic airflow keeps the dirt inside rotating to ensure optimal, high suction power and cleaning performance that lasts.
The Philips Mini Vac, with its powerful motor, is exceptionally quiet thanks to its special streamlined design. The comfortable noise level allows you to tidy up your home any time you want to.
The Philips Mini Vac is also easy to maintain. If the nozzle needs cleaning, you simply put it in the dishwasher. That way you’ve always got a spotless, dirt-free Mini Vac at hand.

KeyBenefitArea.KeyBenefitAreaName: Ideal anywhere - even in your car!

Feature.FeatureName: Brush tool, bendable crevice tool and car plug
Feature.FeatureLongDescription: Brush tool, bendable crevice tool and car plug
Feature.FeatureGlossary: The FC6092 (12V) includes a special car-cleaning kit with car plug for unlimited runtime, which means consumers can clean their cars thoroughly in one go. This model also comes with an extra-long, flexible crevice tool for easy cleaning around car seats and other hard-to-reach areas.

Feature.FeatureName: Smart-design charging base for wall or table
Feature.FeatureLongDescription: Smart-design charging base for wall or table
Feature.FeatureGlossary: You can store the Philips Mini Vac on a convenient charging base, against a wall or on a table. This means the Philips Mini Vac, with its powerful rechargeable battery, is always ready when you are.

The Philips Mini Vac’s cyclonic airflow keeps the dirt inside rotating to ensure optimal, high suction power and lasting cleaning performance. And its 2-stage filtration system ensures that, once inside, the dirt cannot escape. The first filter blocks most dirt, while the pleated, second filter traps the finer dust particles.

Product.MarketingTextHeader: Rechargeable, compact, lightweight sweeper with electric rotating brush for quick, in-between, hassle-free floor cleaning. Sweeps all hard floors and short-pile carpets.

Feature.FeatureGlossary: The unique dust management system gets rid of dirt, from the floor to the bin, effortlessly. One click of a button opens the chamber,allowing you to empty everything inside straight into the bin without bending down or touching any dirt.

Feature.FeatureName: Up to 25 minutes of cordless power on hard floors
Feature.FeatureLongDescription: Up to 25 minutes of cordless cleaning power on hard floors
Feature.FeatureGlossary: Enjoy optimal freedom of movement without a cord getting in your way. Powerful, rechargeable batteries give you up to 25 minutes of cleaning on hard floors.

KeyBenefitArea.KeyBenefitAreaName: Easy to grab, use and store

Feature.FeatureGlossary: At 1.8 kilograms, the Philips Electric Sweeper is light enough to just grab and go. Its compact design lets you clean even those hard-to-reach places. The unique design and smart ‘hang-eye’ feature make the Electric Sweeper easy to store, even in ‘tight’ spaces.

KeyBenefitArea.KeyBenefitAreaName: Sweeps hard floors and short-pile carpets

Feature.FeatureName: Rotating brush sweeps up the dirt
Feature.FeatureLongDescription: Rotating brush sweeps up the dirt
Feature.FeatureGlossary: To make your work easier, an electrically rotating brush automatically flips dirt into the Electric Sweeper’s self-contained dirt chamber. Turn on the Electric Sweeper and effortlessly pick up dirt, crumbs, hair and more. This dynamic brush-roll action is safe and effective on any hard or short-pile carpeted floor in your home.
